[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":422},["ShallowReactive",2],{"article-1":3},{"article":4,"parsedContent":10,"success":421},["Reactive",5],{"articleId":6,"title":7,"content":8,"menuId":6,"menuName":9},1,"系統設定","\u003Ch2>顯示設定\u003C/h2>\r\n\u003Cp>\u003Cimg style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" src=\"https://baihunas.synology.me:4443/uploads/c13f63311a96d6f2.webp\" alt=\"顯示設定\" data-image-id=\"12\">\u003C/p>\r\n\u003Cul>\r\n\u003Cli>解析度可依照自身螢幕與使用習慣調整。\u003C/li>\r\n\u003Cli>若使用高解析度螢幕，建議依照推薦調整介面尺寸，介面才不會太小。\u003C/li>\r\n\u003C/ul>\r\n\u003Cp>\u003Cimg style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" src=\"https://baihunas.synology.me:4443/uploads/fa67f86a0d97396d.webp\" alt=\"顯示設定2\" data-image-id=\"13\">\u003C/p>\r\n\u003Cul>\r\n\u003Cli>偵數限制\u003Cbr>越高越順但電腦也會越熱，推薦最低設定為 \u003Cspan style=\"color: #e67e23;\">60\u003C/span>，或&nbsp;\u003Cspan style=\"color: #e67e23;\">主顯示器的更新率&nbsp;\u003C/span>自動套用螢幕設定。\u003C/li>\r\n\u003Cli>☑非啟動時偵數限制\u003C/li>\r\n\u003Cli>☑離開時偵數限制\u003Cbr>螢幕切出或閒置時將偵數降至約 \u003Cspan style=\"color: #e67e23;\">14~16\u003C/span>，降低電腦發熱。\u003C/li>\r\n\u003C/ul>\r\n\u003Ch2>聲音設定\u003C/h2>\r\n\u003Cp>\u003Cimg style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" src=\"https://baihunas.synology.me:4443/uploads/f658a06f061bc7a5.webp\" alt=\"聲音設置1\" data-image-id=\"14\">\u003C/p>\r\n\u003Cul>\r\n\u003Cli>\u003Cspan style=\"color: #236fa1;\">聲音在非啟動狀態仍然有效\u003C/span>：\u003Cbr>視窗切出後是否仍播放聲音，依照個人習慣設定。\u003C/li>\r\n\u003Cli>\u003Cspan style=\"color: #236fa1;\">騎乘狀態下播放音樂\u003C/span>：\u003Cbr>坐騎會有專屬音樂，若不想聽可取消勾選，就會撥放原本的地圖背景音樂。\u003C/li>\r\n\u003C/ul>\r\n\u003Cp>\u003Cimg style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" src=\"https://baihunas.synology.me:4443/uploads/e08a51e3aacb6520.webp\" alt=\"聲音設置2\" data-image-id=\"15\">\u003C/p>\r\n\u003Cul>\r\n\u003Cli>\u003Cspan style=\"color: #236fa1;\">調節音量\u003C/span>：\u003Cbr>此處的「\u003Cspan style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">語音\u003C/span>」指的是 \u003Cspan style=\"color: #e03e2d;\">NPC 的語音對話\u003C/span>，建議調高一點，喜歡劇情的話辨認是誰在說話在後期很重要！！\u003C/li>\r\n\u003C/ul>\r\n\u003Ch2>圖像設定\u003C/h2>\r\n\u003Cp>\u003Cimg style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" src=\"https://baihunas.synology.me:4443/uploads/1569b8c298e33c60.webp\" alt=\"圖像設置1\" data-image-id=\"16\">\u003C/p>\r\n\u003Cul>\r\n\u003Cli>\u003Cspan style=\"color: #236fa1;\">介面解析度\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>如果螢幕為 2K 以上設定&nbsp;\u003Cspan style=\"color: #e67e23;\">高解析度\u003C/span>，其餘依電腦效能與喜好調整。\u003C/li>\r\n\u003C/ul>\r\n\u003Cp>\u003Cimg style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" src=\"https://baihunas.synology.me:4443/uploads/167e178f28c6e14b.webp\" alt=\"圖像設置2\" data-image-id=\"17\">\u003C/p>\r\n\u003Cul>\r\n\u003Cli>\u003Cspan style=\"color: #236fa1;\">畫面特效\u003C/span>：\u003Cbr>「\u003Cspan style=\"color: #e67e23;\">臨邊昏暗\u003C/span>」與「\u003Cspan style=\"color: #e67e23;\">徑向模糊\u003C/span>」我自己是關閉，整個畫面都會比較亮又乾淨。\u003C/li>\r\n\u003C/ul>\r\n\u003Ch2>滑鼠設定\u003Cbr>\u003Cimg style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" src=\"https://baihunas.synology.me:4443/uploads/b985f06ef703092f.webp\" alt=\"滑鼠設置\" data-image-id=\"18\">\u003C/h2>\r\n\u003Cul>\r\n\u003Cli>全部依照個人習慣調整。\u003C/li>\r\n\u003C/ul>\r\n\u003Ch2>顏色主題設定\u003C/h2>\r\n\u003Cp>\u003Cimg style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" src=\"https://baihunas.synology.me:4443/uploads/f9fc78547d41d742.webp\" alt=\"顏色主題設置1\" data-image-id=\"19\">\u003C/p>\r\n\u003Cul>\r\n\u003Cli>全部依照個人習慣調整。\u003C/li>\r\n\u003C/ul>\r\n\u003Ch2>其他設定\u003C/h2>\r\n\u003Cp>\u003Cimg style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" src=\"https://baihunas.synology.me:4443/uploads/f2fb86858f2c54e7.webp\" alt=\"其他設置\" data-image-id=\"20\">\u003C/p>\r\n\u003Cul>\r\n\u003Cli>\u003Cspan style=\"color: #236fa1;\">自動離開設置\u003C/span>：\u003Cbr>\u003Cspan style=\"color: #ba372a;\">自動切換為離開狀態的時間 在這邊設定。\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003Cspan style=\"color: #ba372a;\">自動切換為離開狀態的時間 在這邊設定。\u003C/span>\u003Cbr>\u003Cspan style=\"color: #ba372a;\">自動切換為離開狀態的時間 在這邊設定。\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\r\n\u003Cli>\u003Cspan style=\"color: #236fa1;\">標題畫面設置\u003C/span>：\u003Cbr>設定為 \u003Cspan style=\"color: #e67e23;\">依照主線進度變化\u003C/span>。\u003C/li>\r\n\u003C/ul>\r\n\u003Ch2>輔助功能設定\u003C/h2>\r\n\u003Cp>\u003Cimg style=\"max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" src=\"https://baihunas.synology.me:4443/uploads/a2f56bff954e5248.webp\" alt=\"協助工具設置1\" data-image-id=\"21\">\u003C/p>\r\n\u003Cul>\r\n\u003Cli>正常人用不到的設定。\u003C/li>\r\n\u003C/ul>","設定調整",{"data":11,"body":13,"toc":411},{"title":12,"description":12},"",{"type":14,"children":15},"root",[16,24,35,50,59,111,116,125,158,167,199,204,213,236,245,276,290,298,303,312,319,324,333,389,394,403],{"type":17,"tag":18,"props":19,"children":21},"element","h2",{"id":20},"顯示設定",[22],{"type":23,"value":20},"text",{"type":17,"tag":25,"props":26,"children":27},"p",{},[28],{"type":17,"tag":29,"props":30,"children":34},"img",{"style":31,"src":32,"alt":20,"dataImageId":33},"max-width: 100%; height: auto;","https://baihunas.synology.me:4443/uploads/c13f63311a96d6f2.webp","12",[],{"type":17,"tag":36,"props":37,"children":38},"ul",{},[39,45],{"type":17,"tag":40,"props":41,"children":42},"li",{},[43],{"type":23,"value":44},"解析度可依照自身螢幕與使用習慣調整。",{"type":17,"tag":40,"props":46,"children":47},{},[48],{"type":23,"value":49},"若使用高解析度螢幕，建議依照推薦調整介面尺寸，介面才不會太小。",{"type":17,"tag":25,"props":51,"children":52},{},[53],{"type":17,"tag":29,"props":54,"children":58},{"style":31,"src":55,"alt":56,"dataImageId":57},"https://baihunas.synology.me:4443/uploads/fa67f86a0d97396d.webp","顯示設定2","13",[],{"type":17,"tag":36,"props":60,"children":61},{},[62,89,94],{"type":17,"tag":40,"props":63,"children":64},{},[65,67,71,73,80,82,87],{"type":23,"value":66},"偵數限制",{"type":17,"tag":68,"props":69,"children":70},"br",{},[],{"type":23,"value":72},"越高越順但電腦也會越熱，推薦最低設定為 ",{"type":17,"tag":74,"props":75,"children":77},"span",{"style":76},"color: #e67e23;",[78],{"type":23,"value":79},"60",{"type":23,"value":81},"，或 ",{"type":17,"tag":74,"props":83,"children":84},{"style":76},[85],{"type":23,"value":86},"主顯示器的更新率 ",{"type":23,"value":88},"自動套用螢幕設定。",{"type":17,"tag":40,"props":90,"children":91},{},[92],{"type":23,"v